{"tid":425501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小行星撞擊雲南　NASA：爆炸相當於540噸TNT","createTime":"2017-10-05T18:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T03:51:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"f19d8be1f3bb7f4321f00079c5a75e60dc07ce49","tid":425501,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T18:57:49.000Z","msg":"10月05日(四) 10:11<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171005/photo/bkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001_01p.jpg?20171005144643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171005144643&h=b23611ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據美國太空總署（NASA）的中文微博稱，香港時間周三（4日）晚上8時07分05秒，地球發生一次小行星撞擊事件，撞擊地點為雲南香格里拉市西北40公里處，爆炸當量相當於540噸TNT黃色炸藥，比2014年的內蒙古錫林格勒事件（450噸）略強。<br />\n<br />\n由於空爆高度不足40公里非常低，因此有隕石在未燃盡前就落到地面的可能性。小行星相對地球的速度為每秒14.6公里，空爆高度只有37公里，很可能有未燃盡的隕石落到地面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171005/photo/bkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001_02p.jpg?20171005144643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20171005144643&h=ea28b8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2014年11月5日凌晨4時14左右，小行星在內蒙古錫林郭勒盟上空爆炸，令夜空光如白晝。（資料圖片）</span><br />\n2014年11月5日凌晨4時14左右，一顆疑似小行星在北京以北約250公里處（地處錫林郭勒盟）上空爆炸，釋放能量相當於500噸TNT炸藥。據NASA當年公布，該顆爆炸的小行星估計最大亮度應在-21等左右，比滿月還要亮得多。<br />\n<br />\n另中國地震台網通報，當晚8時9分錄到一次隕石墜地撞擊事件，位置在雲南省西北部，撞擊威力相當於一次2.1級地震，美國NASA網站也有相關紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171005/bkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171005%2Fbkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001.html&d=iZJlOYnniq6LZk5pHvb61QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=06d8dfba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171005/bkncn-20171005101137331-1005_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b9a57acce9764e8a4cc6132996ff9968f440b4b6","tid":425501,"uid":33543,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:01:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"73047ffbf9545d3b0a7e597105408ea480dc8685","tid":425501,"uid":127272,"like":3,"dislike":92,"score":-89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">線</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ef3f6c14ae778e1c19c7e8a623d624d00ed23cc","tid":425501,"uid":128101,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"撞死哂就啱嫁拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abfbb832f50f68906c9d77425bf83dcd76754d6","tid":425501,"uid":129658,"like":7,"dislike":58,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">線</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得</span></span>"},{"pid":"57775ba83a99b0665174c2e0a2ddb29357d2164a","tid":425501,"uid":11753,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">滅</span></span>"},{"pid":"74784f4c31944a8827132913101198b20a209e1a","tid":425501,"uid":78700,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18